h=ad922f29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.職業殺手契夫（傑森&middot;史塔森飾）為了心愛的未婚妻伊娃（艾咪&middot;史瑪特飾）打算金盆洗手，但是人在江湖飄，哪有不挨刀，就在他想退出江湖時，仇家上門報復，而且是非常特異的手法：在他睡夢中注射一種毒藥，要讓他心臟麻痺而死。契夫在痛苦中求救，終於發現了暫保活命的方法，作極其激烈的運動，讓心臟猛跳，只要心跳一減緩，他就會死。他要如何保住小命，救出被擄走的愛人呢？<br />\n<br />\n2.上一次大難不死的職業殺手契夫（傑森&middot;史塔森飾）又遇到艱辛萬倍的挑戰，有人將他的心臟奪走，改以一個人工幫浦取代，甚至還有一個不知名的華人黑道組織要取他器官，而這次契夫要一直為自己的幫浦心臟充電，否則就會一命不保，所以他竭盡腦汁，用了變電箱、汽車電池、電擊棒，甚至是靜電來維繫生命，究竟他要如何保住性命，追回自己的心臟呢？<br />\n<br />\n11 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=5ae044f4\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU34HMPoqNxaa4E9h32y1mRE%3D&h=ecd93e49\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d1479086ee4067333d25b9ec47a382377622dbb","tid":2245960,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T15:48:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5d006770efe92cd75c92a288a4b094200933a6","tid":2245960,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T15:48:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"42f020970230ed9d53079346307043c04ed4a927","tid":2245960,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T16:35:11.000Z","msg":"<